{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you know, this is hametz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is the day before Passover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The apartment was supposed to be clean already from everything that has to do with bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother nearly died from fright.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she couldn't tell him, [NON-ENGLISH], don't tell our mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Apparently, he was smart enough not to tell her that, because this would have been-- this, my grandmother couldn't comprehend, even though she knew that her daughter was not religious.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But to bake cookies the day before Passover, this is worse than murder, for her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Apparently, he didn't tell her because there was never anything in the family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, this uncle of mine, [NON-ENGLISH], he was the apple of my grandfather's eye.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a gorgeous-looking guy, tall, the payots down to here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember his fingers, long, beautiful fingers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He went to yeshiva, and he was a tremendous scholar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was called that tragic Thursday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He went out some way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They caught him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They took him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Germans caught him in the street, just with another group of people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were sent away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This broke my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was the greatest tragedy to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And another incident, which has to do something with my parents not being religious-- we were there in April [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of 1941.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "April 13 is my birthday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was never prepared nor did I ever have a bar mitzvah, because my parents were not religious.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I remember sitting at the table with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
